### Enhancements

* Add dependency cooldown support via the `cooldown` configuration parameter and `--cooldown` / `--cooldown-days` CLI flags. When enabled, packages with a repodata timestamp more recent than the configured cooldown period are excluded from the solver, giving security vendors time to flag malicious packages before they are installed. A `cooldown_exclude` parameter allows exempting trusted packages. (#15759)

